Package model

Class appointmentsModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.appointmentsModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    reportsDAO
    public class appointmentsModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The Appointments class represents an appointment entity in the system. It contains information about the appointment such as ID, title, description, location, type, start time, end time, associated customer ID, user ID, and contact ID. The class provides a constructor to initialize the appointment with the specified values and getters to retrieve the appointment's attributes.
